{"tid":1950043,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"股東大會只予不多於兩位股東入座 股東爆SEED報警求助","createTime":"2020-03-30T05:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T09:07:59.000Z","uid":253829,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"157184330c5270d3a8f6364d47c6a84cf7a87e33","tid":1950043,"uid":253829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:34:02.000Z","msg":"行政會議已通過推行2條新規例，分別禁止多於4個人的聚集，及管制餐廳營運模式並關閉娛樂場所，於昨日生效。至於上市公司召開股東周年大會（AGM）則可獲豁免，但證監會向業界提到，股東特別大會（EGM）將不獲豁免。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/vaCqkfCg9I56k-U9ZJfh50QzD9g=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/7GTTUIT57O2G3IGNNDQIFBJAC4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FvaCqkfCg9I56k-U9ZJfh50QzD9g%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2F7GTTUIT57O2G3IGNNDQIFBJAC4.jpg&h=54f8e1a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日部份公司已表明，股東大會將會取消或延期，但仍有公司如期召開大會。世紀娛樂國際（959）昨公佈，EGM如期今日於灣仔瑞安中心舉行。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》到現場發現，開會前10分鐘，已逾5個股東到達。惟辦公室門口張貼告示，指「只可予不多於兩位股東入座」，負責職員表示由於人數已滿，稱「要入面啲人出嚟先入得，想入去要等好耐。」大部份股東接收公司贈送的餅卡便離去，有股東離開前稱欲使用洗手間都被拒絕。<br />\n部份股東表示不滿，大呼：「噚晚7點幾出通告話照開，嚟到又唔畀入，開埋啲閉門會議！」其中一位女股東更指：「當我哋啲股東係乜！個會應該取消，垃圾公司！」<br />\n<br />\n之後更有股東報警，4名警員到達現場，有股東稱：「呢度超過4個人，有人非法集結！」不過，在場警員向職員表示：「基本上你地公司開會、私人開會係唔受呢個限制，你哋超過4個人又好，超過5個人又好，我哋係唔會干涉你哋公司開會。」擾攘一輪後，警方停留約20分鐘便離去。<br />\n<br />\n世紀娛樂職員表示，原定已讓女股東入內，但她一直拒絕進場，警察到場後更稱公司不予她進內，與事實不符。<br />\n<br />\n新規例指，如有人在規例生效期間，仍然參與多於4人聚集，將會定額罰款2,000元，或按情況罰款最高25,000元及監禁6個月。<br />\n<br />\n記者 梁延宇"},{"pid":"99c8da176a720a0cab9de0d6b0a6237005859488","tid":1950043,"uid":325840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"今日下午有大量還押手足上庭跪求聲援<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1949806\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1949806</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"aa7a7a1200fda3f951db53103b9a396ebdeefa0a","tid":1950043,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"「呢度超過4個人，有人非法集結！」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbbfa7ab335042757e600cc7b45ce023e17260d6","tid":1950043,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:59:20.000Z","msg":"立法會選舉呢？"},{"pid":"a69802e8fe97fa869c87b9f719b1a5ee8541f56a","tid":1950043,"uid":52881,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:00:52.000Z","msg":"又玩鳩班狗<br />\n好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08a2860a6b5a077bd7aed448c355c3313d5279f7","tid":1950043,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:01:06.000Z","msg":"股東開會都唔得？"},{"pid":"b739f40e08a1fc81a314c5af2563138e8f1d9e54","tid":1950043,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:01:30.000Z","msg":"係咪即係街市偉同崩牙駒間嘢？"},{"pid":"fe772dfa25c33c5bbd248f5272463cbe0bf6360f","tid":1950043,"uid":274722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T06:01:41.000Z","msg":"冇點心食了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"739ddd162aa1b026786c1898a968140de290b797","tid":1950043,"uid":58570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T09:07:59.000Z","msg":"「只可予不多於兩位股東入座」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}